# Gifts4U

**Gifts4U** is a simple and easy-to-use website designed as part of a university assignment for Christmas. It helps users find gift ideas for different people based on categories. The website is built to make the gift-selection process simple and enjoyable, providing users with recommendations suited to different preferences and occasions. The goal of this project was to create a functional and visually appealing website while improving web development skills.  

## Purpose of the Project  

This project was created as part of a university assignment to practice web development skills. The aim was to build the front-end of an e-commerce website that sells Christmas-related gifts. The website follows basic UI/UX principles to ensure clarity and ease of use.  

The assignment helped in improving skills related to designing and structuring web pages and using JavaScript for interactivity. It also provided hands-on experience in building a simple yet effective project from start to finish.

## Technologies Used  

Gifts4U is built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  

- **HTML** is used to create the structure of the web pages.  
- **CSS** is applied for styling, including layout, colors, and fonts, to give the site a festive and attractive appearance.  
- **JavaScript** is included for interactivity, allowing smoother navigation and user-friendly features.  

All code is written in a simple way, making it easy to understand and modify if needed.
